## ğŸ¯ How It Works

**First Visit:**
- User sees login screen
- Enters password: `MySecretPass123`
- Checks "Remember me" (optional)
- Gets access to app

**Return Visits:**
- If "Remember me" was checked â†’ Goes straight in
- If not â†’ Must login again

**Logout:**
- Click "Logout" in nav
- Returns to login screen
- Clears authentication

